            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Apollini <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Sentius <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Serg</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Maurianus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Italic</abbr><ex>ensis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>aedil</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> IIvir augur perpetuus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>colon</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ital</abbr><ex>icae</ex></expan> ex <expan><abbr>arg</abbr><ex>enti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ondo</ex></expan> C <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ono</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Stein war vermutlich sekundär in der Porticus als Konsole vermauert. Wahrscheinlich diente der Stein ursprünglich als Statuenbasis, da oben noch Standspuren erkennbar sind.</p>
            </div>
